blinkd (0.4.8-0.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New version, now under GPL3.
  * Added swedish translation (closes: #348192).
  * Added LSB comments to init script (closes: #349964).
  * Bumped standards version (no changes).
  * Orphaned package, set maintainer to QA.
  * Removed docbook-website build dependency (no changes).
  * Added intltool build dependency.

 -- W. Martin Borgert <debacle@debian.org>  Fri, 18 Jan 2008 09:51:39 +0000

blinkd (0.4.7-1.1) unstable; urgency=low

